│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ A similar issue was reported in the LLVM bug tracker (https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/issues/55895). The fix for that issue involved changing how the insertion point is determined │
│ when building operand vectors. Specifically, it involved ensuring that the insertion point for `insertelement` instructions dominates all the uses of the vector being built.            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
